    <briefdescription>
<para>Component that tracks the revision of a specific <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1timing_1_1GameTimer" kindref="compound">GameTimer</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Entities with this component observe a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1timing_1_1GameTimer" kindref="compound">GameTimer</ref> identified by its <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1core_1_1data_1ab4fb083d208d1dc824881ed9fd012f46" kindref="member">GameTimerId</ref>. The stored revision can be compared against the timer&apos;s current revision to detect updates.</para>
